milestones.description: Wettimuny and Fernando's 101-run partnership is SL's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 71 between Wettimuny and Fernando
Madugalle and Ranatunga's 69-run partnership is SL's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 57 between Duleep Mendis and Ranasinghe
de Silva and Ranatunga's 35-run partnership is SL's highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 29 between de Mel and Ratnayeke
Greg Chappell has scored 17 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, breaking Greenidge's record
